FBIS3-60690 "jptnd002___94018" JPRS-TND-94-002 Document Type:JPRS Document Title:PROLIFERATION ISSUES 18 January 1994 LATIN AMERICA CAYMAN ISLANDS Containers With Radioactive Waste Seized From Ship PY2412122593 Brasilia Radio Nacional da Amazonia Network in Portuguese 0900 GMT 24 Dec 93 PY2412122593 Brasilia Radio Nacional da Amazonia Network Language: Portuguese Article Type:BFN [Text] Experts from the Rio Grande do Sul, RS, State Foundation for Environmental Protection seized 32 containers with clandestine radioactive waste. The cargo was transferred to warehouse A5 in Rio Grande Port, which was designed to store dangerous material. On 27 December, the experts will test the contents with radiation-measuring equipment and investigate the rest of the cargo being carried by the ship Belatrix, where the containers were found.
